 Used**:\n  - Enrollment totals (by gender)\n  - Number of schools and teachers (by gender)\n  - Repetition rates\n  - Provincial breakdowns\n\n---\n\n### üõ†Ô∏è Methodology\n- The data was cleaned and filtered to extract key indicators related to:\n  - **Enrollment Equity**: % of girls enrolled vs total\n  - **Staffing Representation**: % of female teachers\n  - **Education Quality Proxy**: Repeat rates\n  - **Resource Burden**: Student‚ÄìTeacher ratios\n\n- Charts were created using **Python (Pandas, Seaborn, Matplotlib)**.\n- All calculations (e.g., % Female Teachers) were performed using pandas transformations.\n\n---\n\n### üìä Key Indicators Visualized\n1. % of girls enrolled by province  \n2. % of female teachers by province  \n3. % of repeaters who are girls  \n4. Total vs girls‚Äô enrollment  \n5. Total vs female teachers  \n6. Overall repeat rate  \n7. Student‚Äìteacher ratio  \n8. Female teacher share (thresholds)  \n9. Enrollment vs school availability  \n10. Heatmap of gender indicators  ","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Re-import libraries after kernel reset\nimport pandas as pd\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nimport seaborn as sns\n\n# Reload the previously processed dataset\neducation_df = pd.read_csv('/kaggle/input/cambodia-education-cleaned/cleaned_cambodia_education_2020_2021.csv')\n\n# Set common visual style\nsns.set(style=\"whitegrid\")\nplt.rcParams[\"figure.figsize\"] = (12, 6)\n","metadata":{"_uuid":"051d70d956493feee0c6d64651c6a088724dca2a","_execution_state":"idle","trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2025-03-31T10:14:04.75332Z","iopub.execute_input":"2025-03-31T10:14:04.75404Z","iopub.status.idle":"2025-03-31T10:14:04.77669Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2025-03-31T10:14:04.75401Z","shell.execute_reply":"2025-03-31T10:14:04.775717Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# Chart 1: % Girls Enrolled by Province\nplt.figure()\nsns.barplot(data=education_df.sort_values('% Girls E